item.title: Las Vegas Raiders Honor Late Hall Of Famer Jim Otto With Helmet Decal
item.description: The Las Vegas Raiders have added a decal to the back of their helmets in honor of late Hall of Fame center Jim Otto, who passed away in May at the age of 86.
